{"tid":631191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被指性侵鄭爽 陳嘉上願對質：否則我將公開追究","createTime":"2018-04-16T08:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T02:22:15.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3049f19ef27adfbef4ef9600c5057a3e3b97bc","tid":631191,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"著名導演陳嘉上今午在微博留言，指近日自己聽聞有位知名女星，指他當年曾威脅兼性侵內地女星鄭爽，而陳嘉上和鄭爽曾於2011年合作拍電影《畫壁》，陳嘉上在微博說：「聞最近一位知名女星在朋友談話中，指我當年曾威脅鄭爽且性侵等等。一位朋友找上我友求證。我原對此等八卦胡編並不重視，但話出自一位尊貴的女星之口我不得不重視。不知這女士從何處得到這消息，我很願意和她對質。若不敢站出來説話就請立即停止這等不負責任的言論，否則我將再公開追究。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180416/s00009/06e34e9ed291bc2fd516fe15939f2f3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180416%2Fs00009%2F06e34e9ed291bc2fd516fe15939f2f3a.jpg&h=8db6fe6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e41cecbb0c7b753050d414fcb4d3da3dcf72dff0","tid":631191,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"陳爽粒的"},{"pid":"2df72b5155531ce547470f5c44143908675b32d6","tid":631191,"uid":48577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"以為陳爽同鄭嘉穎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a1c171df59238601dff3001ac1be6047ec7ac7","tid":631191,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"陳大導叫完雞唔記得比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79a6f35aacc0d8e073a679a8809962932a8b7d8","tid":631191,"uid":74085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"鄭爽整容整到，又瘦到棚骨咁"},{"pid":"3c7a2153045e1c52731abdc28b5b0e3171fc6ef0","tid":631191,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"照計以陳導既名氣在大6可以大把野食，洗鬼性侵女星咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ebdeaa2ea44d23143c1813cf89668401610bbf"